api.bin

# Local-stack scratch space.
.env.local
.data/
.cache/

# Generated Rust/TS code (`crates/*/src/{_gen,gen}/`,
# `crates/server/src/connect_gen/`) is intentionally COMMITTED for this reference
# example, so a checkout builds without running `just regen` and reviewers can
# read the generated output. It is still re-derived from `proto/` — do not edit
# by hand. Add the paths back here if you prefer a regen-on-checkout workflow.

# The browser WASM client, by contrast, is a binary build artifact from
# `just build-wasm` (wasm-pack) — regenerated, not committed.
frontend/src/wasm/
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/